00:12:05,104 --> 00:12:07,844
Tapi memang benar kau mencurigakan.

200
00:12:08,054 --> 00:12:11,033
Jangan asal tuduh kalau tidak punya bukti.

201
00:12:11,034 --> 00:12:13,583
